B-I.xyz           Benzene form I
B-II.xyz          Benzene form II
G-A.xyz           Glycine form alpha
G-B.xyz           Glycine form beta
G-G.xyz           Glycine form gamma
S-A.xyz           Succinic acid alpha
S-B.xyz           Succinic acid beta


In order to conver the files  into an XYZ format
read by i-PI use the script:

``

get_ipi_xyz_from_libatom_xyz.py B-I.xyz B-I-ipi.xyz
get_ipi_xyz_from_libatom_xyz.py B-II.xyz B-II-ipi.xyz
get_ipi_xyz_from_libatom_xyz.py G-A.xyz G-A-ipi.xyz
get_ipi_xyz_from_libatom_xyz.py G-B.xyz G-B-ipi.xyz
get_ipi_xyz_from_libatom_xyz.py G-G.xyz G-G-ipi.xyz
get_ipi_xyz_from_libatom_xyz.py S-A.xyz S-A-ipi.xyz
get_ipi_xyz_from_libatom_xyz.py S-B.xyz S-B-ipi.xyz


``

